you see, when we say Prana
Pratishta: Prana means the life force,
当我们说Prana Pratishta：Prana意味着生命力

15
00:01:19,666 --> 00:01:22,422
Pratishta means
installing the life force.
Pratishta意味着注入生命力

16
00:01:24,550 --> 00:01:29,266
When one is doing the prayer
当一个人在做着注入生命力的祈祷

17
00:01:29,660 --> 00:01:34,511
of installing this life force,
it doesn’t mean that God is not there.
它不意味着神不在那里

18
