But humans are fools
sometimes due to Maya.
但是由于摩耶人们有时是愚蠢的

27
00:02:29,730 --> 00:02:33,866
So, Prana Pratishta,
所以 注入生命力仪式

28
00:02:34,350 --> 00:02:38,244
not everybody can
do Prana Pratishta.
不是每个人都能做注入生命力仪式

29
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:41,088
Firstly, you have to understand
that. There are many people,
首先 你必须理解那 有很多人

30
00:02:41,170 --> 00:02:44,488
many priests who say, "Yes, we have
done the prayer of Prana Pratishta,
很多牧师说 是的 我们已经做了注入生命力仪式的祈祷

31
00:02:44,730 --> 00:02:48,844
that’s it, you know, the murti is blessed
