in the outside so that you can
去接受 在外面显现祂自己所以你可以

45
00:03:53,711 --> 00:03:57,977
build a relationship, an easy
relationship one to one.
建立一个关系 一个简单的一对一的关系

46
00:03:59,460 --> 00:04:02,466
Very often you see people,
yes, look for God inside of you,
通常你看人们 是的 寻找你内在的神

47
00:04:02,620 --> 00:04:07,422
but which part of you, you will look for God?
Where would you look for God? In your heart?
但哪部分的你 你将寻找神 你在哪里寻找神 在你的心中

48
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:10,730
No, you can’t find
God in your heart.
不 你不能在你的心中找到神

49
00:04:11,755 --> 00:04:13,888
Otherwise doctor
would have already found
否则医生已经找到了

50
