certain texts say,
yes, it is here
某些文献 是的 在这里

56
00:04:46,066 --> 00:04:48,866
in the middle, not on the
left side, but in the middle.
正中间 不是在左边 是在正中间

57
00:04:50,133 --> 00:04:52,755
But this is an energy
point, you see,
但是这里是个能量点

58
00:04:54,155 --> 00:04:56,266
your spiritual heart
is an energy point
你的心是一个能量点

59
00:04:57,244 --> 00:05:00,088
and within that energy
point the Lord resides.
并且神居住在那能量内

60
00:05:02,555 --> 00:05:04,777
So, how small He is.
所以 祂是如此的小

61
00:05:07,466 --> 00:05:10,955
Here out of love He
made Himself the smallest
这里出于爱祂把祂自己变成最小

62
00:05:12,888 --> 00:05:14,911
and abides within
His creation
并停留在祂的创造中

63
00:05:17,844 --> 00:05:21,000
and at the same time
we are all in Him.
同时我们都在祂里面

64
00:05:21,444 --> 00:05:25,088
You see, when we chant, for example,
Om Namo Narayanaya.
当我们唱诵 Om Namo Narayanaya

65
00:05:25,555 --> 00:05:28,511
The mantra Om Namo Narayanaya,
this is our mantra, no?
颂歌 Om Namo Narayanaya 这是我们的颂歌 不是吗

66
00:05:29,888 --> 00:05:32,422
This mantra has a
great secret in it.
颂歌里有一个很大的秘密

67
00:05:35,977 --> 00:05:43,200
In itself it reminds mankind
of what is one’s duty here.
在它自己里面-它提醒着一个人他的的职责

68
00:05:44,777 --> 00:05:47,200
One’s duty is to
attain the Lord.
一个人的职责是去到达神

69
00:05:47,777 --> 00:05:52,244
Why we have to attain the Lord?
Because we are eternally bound to Him.
为什么我们必须到达神 因为我们永远与祂相连

70
00:05:53,955 --> 00:05:58,488
This is our core duty. The rest
is just a game, a drama,
这是我们的主要的责任 剩下的只是游戏 喜剧

71
00:06:00,288 --> 00:06:02,955
a drama which
we think it is real,
我们认为一个戏剧是真实的

72
