Countless of lives
you have done that.
你已经做过那了无数世

81
00:06:53,688 --> 00:06:56,688
Not one life.
Thousands of lives!
不是一次生命 成千上万世

82
00:06:58,866 --> 00:07:01,911
But why have you not
attained that supreme bliss?
但是为什么你没有到达那最高的喜悦

83
00:07:03,644 --> 00:07:08,088
