supreme bliss, you will eternally dwell with the Lord.
因为一旦你已经到达那最高的喜悦 你将永远和神同在

84
00:07:12,733 --> 00:07:17,333
Because you are looking for Him
elsewhere when He is seated within you.
因为你正在其他地方找祂时祂就坐在你里面

85
00:07:21,533 --> 00:07:27,511
And how to attain Him? Is only when your
mind runs towards Him, not your heart.
并且如何达到祂 只有当你的头脑朝向祂跑时而不是你的心

86
00:07:30,133 --> 00:07:33,222
Very often people say,
"Yes, you know, my heart."
人们经常说 是的 我知道 我的心

87
00:07:35,555 --> 00:07:39,244
You don’t have control over your heart,
but you have control over your mind.
你不能控制你的心 但是你可以控制你的头脑

88
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:44,177
That’s why Krishna said in the Gita,
"Surrender your mind to Me
那就是为什么奎师那在薄伽梵歌中说 放下你的头脑臣服于我

89
00:07:44,577 --> 00:07:48,711
