He didn’t say surrender anything else,
He didn’t say surrender your soul.
祂没有说放下其他一切 祂没有说放下你的灵魂

92
00:07:58,044 --> 00:08:01,755
How can you hold your soul and surrender
it? You can’t. You belong to Him already.
你怎么能留着你的灵魂并丢掉它 你不能 你已经属于祂

93
00:08:03,266 --> 00:08:05,977
What He said? "Surrender
your mind upon to Me."
祂说了什么 向我臣服你的头脑

94
00:08:07,333 --> 00:08:13,511
