some years back.
几年前

115
00:09:51,711 --> 00:09:55,488
He is a great
devotee of Krishna.
他是奎师那的伟大的奉献者

116
00:09:58,755 --> 00:10:01,000
So, one day there was
a big Prana Pratishta.
所以 一天有一个大型的生命力注入的仪式

117
00:10:01,422 --> 00:10:04,866
So, the priest was chanting
all the Vedic mantras, 
所以 神父正在唱诵所有的吠陀颂歌

118
00:10:06,111 --> 00:10:11,422
