123
00:10:36,311 --> 00:10:39,977
placed it in front
of the nostril of the
放在了神像

124
00:10:42,177 --> 00:10:44,088
deity,
的鼻孔中

125
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:50,022
nothing. You see, if you put
a cotton in front of your nose,
什么都没发生 如果你把一块棉花放在你的鼻子面前

126
