"Thakurji is there. Krishna is there
所以 什么也没发生 所以 接着圣人说  塔库里在那里 奎师那在那里

130
00:11:14,066 --> 00:11:17,711
and I am asking Him to
please, bless the deity,
并且我请求祂 祝福这个神像

131
00:11:17,866 --> 00:11:20,844
 enter into the deity."
So, he saw Krishna entering the deity.
进入这个神像 所以 他看到奎师那进入这个神像

132
00:11:21,511 --> 00:11:25,533
So, when he saw Krishna entering the deity,
he said, "Here, you will see the difference."
所以当他看见奎师那进入这个神像 他说 这里 你将看到不同

133
00:11:25,644 --> 00:11:30,177
Then this time when
he put the cotton, He was
接着这一次当他放置了棉花 祂

134
00:11:31,111 --> 00:11:35,577
inhaling and exhaling.
So, the cotton would move.
在呼吸和吸气 所以 棉花可以移动

135
00:11:37,822 --> 00:11:42,466
So, like that, you see, through
the mantras, through the prayers,
所以 像那样 你瞧 通过颂歌 通过祈祷 

136
00:11:42,911 --> 00:11:47,200
through the faith of the people especially,
through the faith of the people,
主要通过通过人们的信心 通过人们的信心

137
00:11:48,422 --> 00:11:52,400
a mere statue which is made
of stone is transformed into
一个纯粹由石头做的雕像可以转化成

